data.description: OFFERING $5,000 CLOSING COSTS TO QUALIFIED BUYER!! Welcome to this beautiful turn-key 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home! This home is in North Columbus and sits on a corner lot of almost one acre. The property is conveniently located to Fort Moore, amenities and everything you may need! This stunning home offers beautiful LVP flooring, quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, a roof that is only a few years old, water heater just over 1 year old, installed privacy backyard fence under a year old, perfect for entertaining and a ton more updates to this home! Literally so much to offer, you won't want to miss it!
